305
00:22:49,653 --> 00:22:54,653
The next morning Mrs. Rottenmeier took over the regiment in the house again.

306
00:22:54,653 --> 00:22:57,653
It was all the same as before the visit of the grandmother.

307
00:22:57,653 --> 00:23:03,653
She scolded every little thing and especially Heidi could not hear a friendly
word from her.

308
00:23:03,653 --> 00:23:08,653
Every morning at ten the Mr. Candidate came and Heidi and Clara had to listen to
him for hours.

309
00:23:08,653 --> 00:23:10,653
It was all no longer fun.

310
00:23:10,653 --> 00:23:14,653
She could not stop playing with the two handpuppets either.

311
00:23:15,403 --> 00:23:21,003
It was as if Mrs. Sesemann from the big house there in the Frankfurter Straße
had also taken the laughter with her.

312
00:23:21,003 --> 00:23:24,403
